HEADWORD: Excentrical
<hw>Ex*cen"tric*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Same as
<er>Eccentric</er>, <er>Eccentrical</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>One-sided; having the normally
central portion not in the true center.</def>
<rj><au>Gray.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Excentricity</ent>⟦br⟧
